\[\begin{pmatrix} x \\ y \\ y \end{pmatrix} \cdot \begin{pmatrix} 1 \\ 2 \\ 2 \end{pmatrix} = 0,\]which gives us $x + 4y = 0.$  Then $x = -4y.$  Substituting into $x^2 + 2y^2 = 9,$ we get
